<L>__{exterior above oahu the dogfight day}
<A>__{the japanese planes are in tight, disciplined formation, their minds on the targets below them in the harbor. but their day of shooting sitting ducks changes as the two p 40's blast in, wing guns blazing, chopping into two zeros. both zeros falter and begin to lose altitude. the p 40's make almost impossible tight turns, still side by side, and go after the two plane they crippled on the first pass. rafe finishes one zero, making it explode in a ball of flame in the air. danny finishes the other, shooting off its wing so that it spirals into the sea and crashes there. the p 40's swoop up again.}
